{"tid":2355320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大炒車前夕  梁齊昕Facebook出「悼文」","createTime":"2021-01-06T04:57:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T06:00:27.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8fa739bc6dc54f8c0349dab179165e90b3b9b3b","tid":2355320,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:57:37.000Z","msg":"全國政協副主席梁振英次女梁齊昕，近年少有在Facebook發文，今（5日）卻突然分享一宗由「HK01 .COM」發出的車禍新聞，又指「我們最好的朋友之一出了車禍希望你安息」，令一眾網友嘩然。後來，她再發另一文表示「Virus/ was hacked !! Sorry to everyone who was tagged. I didn&rsquo;t make such a post !! Apologies !!」，原來是Facebook被黑客入侵，向被「點名」的朋友致歉。<br />\n<br />\n這是新一輪Facebook帳戶密碼詐騙攻擊，黑客近日假扮《香港01》新聞，同時以Facebook發出通知，指你的朋友在發文中標注（Tag）了你，內容是「我們最好的朋友之一出了車禍。希望你安息」，實則是黑客將對出於朋友的關心作為誘餌以入侵帳戶。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/570503</code></pre>"},{"pid":"a8878709caf9beffbc238c04ee553ef1105bc141","tid":2355320,"uid":36383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:57:34.000Z","msg":"智商係遺傳"},{"pid":"f3e0c6d81ed983fecca19e6a34beca5ed27d1f1c","tid":2355320,"uid":13653,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"馬英九看了一下手錶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e0689c5be597e8993f5e4d9a623ab30478cd8df","tid":2355320,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T06:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/27/165620_61771f6669c0209271476cb686a24d13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F27%2F165620_61771f6669c0209271476cb686a24d13.jpg&h=bb2491da&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}